[12976] (w=123)  [3m[38;2;146;131;116mI'm leaning toward a bold, specific direction here. For a design system landing page, I want to avoid the typical purple  [0m]8;;
[12977] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116mgradients and generic card layouts that feel like every other SaaS site. What if I treated this like a precision          [0m]8;;
[12978] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116minstrument—a cockpit dashboard with dense information, dark headers, crisp typography, and a grid-based structure where   [0m]8;;
[12979] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116mevery element serves a clear purpose? The orange becomes a signal color for highlights, blue-p drives interactivity,      [0m]8;;
[12980] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116mblue-q anchors the deeper structure, and gray-lead handles secondary details.[39m[23m                                             [0m]8;;
[12981] (w=123)                                                                                                                            [0m]8;;
[12982] (w=123)  [3m[38;2;146;131;116mBut actually, I think I can push this further. What if I borrowed from editorial design—a newspaper-inspired grid with    [0m]8;;
[12983] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116mbold headlines, tight multi-column packages, and dense information blocks? The blue-q acts like ink on white, orange as   [0m]8;;
[12984] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116man accent color like you'd see in print. That feels more distinctive.[39m[23m                                                     [0m]8;;
[12985] (w=123)                                                                                                                            [0m]8;;
[12986] (w=123)  [3m[38;2;146;131;116mFor the constraint of fitting everything in one viewport, I'm picturing a blueprint dashboard layout: a dark navigation   [0m]8;;
[12987] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116mstrip at the top, then a clean white content area below organized as a tight grid. Left side holds the packages in a      [0m]8;;
[12988] (w=123)  [3;38;2;146;131;116mcompact list, the middle showcases a hero moment with large typography, the right side has quick start and tech info, and [0m]8;;
